# Lab: Group Weekend Routine Plans

> It is Friday and two classmates are planning what their group will do this weekend using the same routine sequence.

## Roles

A: Persona 1
  You lead a group weekend plan and check details

B: Persona 2
  You describe your family/group plan and compare it

## Turns

A: Ask about their group weekend plan
   (Open with plural)
   - Que haran este fin de semana? | What will you all do this weekend?
   hint: Hola! Que haran en familia este fin de semana?

B: Start your sequence with levantarse and desayunar
   (Use nos levantaremos / desayunaremos)
   - Nos levantaremos... | We will get up...
   - Luego desayunaremos... | Then we will have breakfast...
   hint: Nos levantaremos temprano y luego desayunaremos juntos.

A: Ask about work, exercise, and lunch
   (Prompt ellos/ellas)
   - Ellos trabajaran? | Will they work?
   - Ellas haran ejercicio? | Will they exercise?
   - Y ustedes almorzaran juntos? | And will you all have lunch together?
   hint: Despues ellos trabajaran, ellas haran ejercicio y ustedes almorzaran?

B: Answer with working block
   (Use group forms and one yo naturally)
   - Ellos trabajaran... | They will work...
   - Ellas haran ejercicio... | They will exercise...
   - Almorzaremos... | We will have lunch...
   hint: Si, ellos trabajaran por la manana, ellas haran ejercicio por la tarde y almorzaremos al mediodia. Yo cocinare.

A: Ask how they will finish the day
   (Move to night)
   - Y por la noche que haran? | And what will you all do at night?
   - Cenaran en casa? | Will you all have dinner at home?
   hint: Y por la noche cenaran, veran la tele y dormiran temprano?

B: Close with cenar, ver la tele, dormir
   (Complete with future simple + one yo line)
   - Cenaremos... | We will have dinner...
   - Veremos la tele... | We will watch TV...
   - Dormiremos... | We will sleep...
   hint: Cenaremos a las ocho, veremos la tele un rato y dormiremos temprano. Yo cerrare la cocina.

A: Invite them to match plans
   (Finish together)
   - Querran hacer el mismo plan? | Will you all want to do the same plan?
   - Nos veremos el sabado! | We will see each other on Saturday!
   hint: Perfecto. Querran hacer el mismo plan con nosotros el sabado?

## Tips

- Prioritize future simple forms (`-e, -as, -a, -emos, -an`) for all action verbs.
- Keep the same sequence: levantarse, desayunar, trabajar, hacer ejercicio, almorzar, cenar, ver la tele, dormir.
- Repeat connectors (despues, luego, por la noche) so your plan sounds organized.
